sequenceDiagram
    participant GW as MarketDataGateway
    participant TICKS as TickStream
    participant EVAL as RuleEvaluator
    participant FIRED as FiredAlertsStream
    participant DISP as AlertDispatcher
    participant IDEM as IdempotencyCache
    participant NOTIF as NotificationSystem

    Note over EVAL: local state co-partitioned by instrument_id<br/>(subs index + last_price + armed flags)

    GW->>TICKS: publish tick {instrument, price, ts} key=instrument_id
    TICKS->>EVAL: consume tick (partition for instrument)
    EVAL->>EVAL: prev = state.last_price[instrument]
    EVAL->>EVAL: state.last_price[instrument] = price
    EVAL->>EVAL: lookup subs[instrument] in local state
    loop for each ARMED sub on instrument
        alt cross detected (prev < threshold, price >= threshold)
            EVAL->>EVAL: alert.state = FIRED (local flag)
            EVAL-)FIRED: emit alert_fired {alert_id, user_id, price, arm_epoch, idem_key}
        else no crossing
            Note over EVAL: skip (no level re-fire)
        end
    end

    FIRED->>DISP: consume fired event
    DISP->>IDEM: SETNX idem:{alert_id}:{arm_epoch} TTL=1h
    alt idem key set (first time)
        IDEM-->>DISP: OK (new)
        DISP->>DISP: check user prefs / quiet hours
        alt within quiet hours
            DISP->>DISP: suppress or defer
        else deliver
            DISP->>NOTIF: dispatch push/email/SMS
            NOTIF-->>DISP: delivered
            DISP->>DISP: update alerts.state = FIRED, last_fired_at
        end
    else duplicate (replay after evaluator restart)
        IDEM-->>DISP: already exists
        DISP-X NOTIF: drop duplicate
    end

    Note over EVAL,DISP: re-arm service reads FIRED stream<br/>schedules delayed re-arm after cooldown_sec<br/>increments arm_epoch on next arming
